OL,3,CCardiff restaurant operator fined more
OL,4,Cthan #20,000 for food hygiene offences
OL,6,FA restaurant operator has been ordered
OL,7,Fto pay #22,549 after a catalogue of
OL,8,Ffailings were found at a restaurant
OL,9,Fand a takeaway in Canton, Cardiff.
OL,11,FEnvironmental Health Officers carried
OL,12,Fout inspections between September and
OL,13,FDecember 2024 and deemed both
OL,14,Fbusinesses as an imminent risk to
OL,15,Fpublic health.
OL,17,FRasathi Sri Lankan Takeaway and
OL,18,FChennai Dosa - two separate food
OL,19,Fbusinesses on Cowbridge Road East -
OL,20,Fare both owned and operated by the
OL,21,Fsame company, JS Local Ltd.
