OL,3,CCardiff restaurant operator fined more
OL,4,Cthan #20,000 for food hygiene offences
OL,6,FJS Local Ltd and the food business
OL,7,Foperator, Jerurasa Senjoansrajah, were
OL,8,Fsentenced at Cardiff Magistrates'
OL,9,FCourt on December 15, following a
OL,10,Fseries of inspections at both premises.
OL,12,FThese inspections resulted in both
OL,13,Fbusinesses being voluntarily closed by
OL,14,Fthe operator due to the risks posed to
OL,15,Fpublic health.
OL,17,FRasathi Sri Lankan Takeaway has two
OL,18,Fdirectors, Jerurasa Senjoansrajah and
OL,19,FSaromina Senjoansrajah, while Chennai
OL,20,FDosa, an Indian restaurant, has one
OL,21,Fdirector: Jerurasa Senjoansrajah
