OL,3,CCardiff restaurant operator fined more
OL,4,Cthan #20,000 for food hygiene offences
OL,6,FOfficers found a widespread rodent
OL,7,Finfestation at both premises, along
OL,8,Fwith poor cleanliness and serious
OL,9,Ffailings in food safety management.
OL,11,FCardiff Council says inspectors
OL,12,Fvisiting Rasathi Sri Lankan Takeaway
OL,13,Fon September 4, 2024 requested basic
OL,14,Ffood safety paperwork - including pest
OL,15,Fcontrol records, allergy
OL,16,Fdocumentation, and staff training
OL,17,Fcertificates - but the operator failed
OL,18,Fto provide any information.
