OL,3,CCardiff restaurant operator fined more
OL,4,Cthan #20,000 for food hygiene offences
OL,6,FBy December 4, 2024, Rasathi Sri
OL,7,FLankan Takeaway had been converted to
OL,8,Ffood storage for Chennai Dosa.
OL,10,FDuring visits in December 2024,
OL,11,FEnvironmental Health Officers
OL,12,Fdiscovered mouse droppings in food
OL,13,Fpreparation areas, dirty equipment,
OL,14,Funrefrigerated food, and an overall
OL,15,Fpoor level of cleanliness.
