OL,3,CCardiff restaurant operator fined more
OL,4,Cthan #20,000 for food hygiene offences
OL,6,FOn December 6, the closure notice for
OL,7,FChennai Dosa was revoked after pest
OL,8,Fproofing and deep cleaning were
OL,9,Fcompleted. However, pest activity and
OL,10,Fpoor food storage practices continued,
OL,11,Fresulting in formal enforcement action
OL,12,Fby SRS under the Prevention of Damage
OL,13,Fby Pests Act 1949.
OL,15,FFollowing this action, Saromina
OL,16,FSenjoansrajh resigned as a director of
OL,17,FRasathi Sri Lankan Takeaway, leaving
OL,18,Fher husband, Jerurasa Senjoansrajh, as
OL,19,Fthe sole food business operator for
OL,20,Fboth premises.
