OL,3,CCardiff restaurant operator fined more
OL,4,Cthan #20,000 for food hygiene offences
OL,6,FCllr Norma Mackie, Cabinet Member
OL,7,Fresponsible for Shared Regulatory
OL,8,FServices at Cardiff Council, said:
OL,10,F"The conditions our officers found at
OL,11,Fthis takeaway and restaurant posed a
OL,12,Fclear and immediate risk to the
OL,13,Fpublic. Basic requirements - such as
OL,14,Feffective pest control, thorough
OL,15,Fcleaning, and robust food safety
OL,16,Fmanagement - were not in place.
