OL,3,CCardiff restaurant operator fined more
OL,4,Cthan #20,000 for food hygiene offences
OL,6,FBusinesses handling highrisk foods,
OL,7,Fincluding rice, chicken, mutton, fish
OL,8,Fand eggs, must have effective pest
OL,9,Fcontrol, robust cleaning and
OL,10,Fdisinfection schedules, and a
OL,11,Fdocumented food safety management
OL,12,Fsystem. Failure to meet these
OL,13,Fstandards endangers customers and will
OL,14,Flead to enforcement action."
OL,16,FJS Local Ltd was fined #16,080 and
OL,17,Fordered to pay #1,084 in costs.
